room_title: Escape room "Murder! Mystery" by Escape NE Ohio in Warren
room_address: 200 Chestnut Avenue Northeast Suite C Warren, OH 44483
room_description: Margaret Cornwall was a 60-year-old English spinster who lived a quiet life in her cottage on the edge of town. Once a week Margaret invites guests over for tea. After her last tea with a few of her friends, Margaret wound up dead. The mode of murder is hidden in the room. Find it and you've found the murderer.
